O=A+\overrightarrow{AB}+\lambda\overrightarrow{HB}\quad (1)
O=A+\overrightarrow{AC}+\mu\overrightarrow{JC}\quad (2)
\overrightarrow{HB}=\vec{c}-[\frac{(\vec{b}\cdot\vec{c})}{b}]\frac{\vec{b}}{b}\quad (3)
